data.description: Welcome to your new home! This stunning property features both stucco and siding, offering a unique and stylish exterior. Inside, you'll find granite countertops in both the kitchen and bathrooms, adding a touch of elegance to every space. Situated on nearly 2 acres of great land within the city limits, this home offers the rare convenience of expansive land, just 20 minutes from downtown Dallas. With sleek laminate floors throughout (no carpet), this home has been beautifully maintained and is ready for you to move in and enjoy.
